      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I have a confession: I used to spend weeks agonizing over travel destinations. Tabs open in every browser window, hotel comparison sites consuming my evenings, Reddit threads about \"hidden gems\" piling up in my bookmarks. The paradox of choice turned what should have been exciting into exhausting.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://www.awin1.com/awclick.php?mid=85831&id=2061927"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Then someone told me about ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Flykube",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", and honestly, it rewired how I think about short getaways.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Flykube is a Spain- and Portugal-based online travel agency that books your entire trip — flights, hotel, the works — while keeping the destination a secret until just before departure. You pick the dates and budget. They pick where you go. It sounds terrifying. It is, in the best possible way.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/what-is-flykube-es-pt"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I have put together this step-by-step walkthrough so you can see exactly how it works, what to expect, and why thousands of travelers across Europe are rating it ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "4.3 out of 5 stars from 2,000+ reviews",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ". Let's dive in.",
