      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "After digging into Flykube's model and talking to repeat users, here are my top recommendations:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Start with a lower tier for your first trip.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " If you are nervous about the surprise element, a €109–€159 city break is a low-risk way to test the waters. The \"worst\" outcome is a perfectly nice European city you had not prioritized.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Be flexible with dates.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " The more date windows you can offer, the better the destination options Flykube can pull from.",
