      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "3. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Check the weather context.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " If you book a Beach Surprise in November, set your expectations for southern destinations. If you book a City Break in December, you might land somewhere with spectacular Christmas markets.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "4. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Read the hotel details once revealed.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Flykube provides hotel information upon reveal. If the hotel does not meet your needs (accessibility, specific preferences), their support team is responsive about discussing options.",
