            "text": "6. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Book with a partner or friend for your first time.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " The shared surprise amplifies the experience. Solo Flykube is great, but revealing a mystery destination with someone else adds a layer of fun.",
