      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "\"Better than expected.\"",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " This phrase appears constantly. Travelers arrive with tempered expectations (it is a budget surprise trip, after all) and consistently report that the hotel quality exceeded what they anticipated for the price.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "\"The reveal was the highlight.\"",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Multiple travelers mention that the moment of finding out the destination was the most memorable part — even more than the trip itself in some cases.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "\"We have rebooked three times now.\"",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Repeat booking rates are high. Once people experience the model, they come back. It becomes a tradition.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "\"Customer service was quick and helpful.\"",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " A few reviews mention needing to adjust dates or having questions about the hotel, and Flykube's support handled it smoothly.",
