        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You pick the frame — dates, budget, airport. They paint the picture. And when that reveal notification lands in your inbox, you get to experience something most adult life does not offer enough: genuine surprise.",
