    "image_prompt": "Editorial tech thumbnail, 16:9. Incorporate the brand logo fetched from https://logo.clearbit.com/flykube.com as the clean focal element over a soft amber-to-cream gradient (Notion + Apple aesthetic). A traveler with a carry-on suitcase standing at a European airport gate, sunlight streaming through large windows, looking at a phone screen with a surprised smile, departure board blurred in the background. Glassmorphism cards, soft volumetric light, generous negative space for a title, no embedded text, no watermark. --ar 16:9 --style raw",
    "faq_items": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
