        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How much does a Flykube surprise trip cost?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Flykube surprise trips start from as low as €109 per person for a city break (flights + hotel included). Beach surprise packages start from €199. Higher budget tiers unlock premium destinations and upgraded hotel options. All prices are all-inclusive with no hidden fees at checkout.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "When do I find out my Flykube destination?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Flykube typically reveals your destination 1 to 3 days before your departure date. You will receive the reveal via email or through the Flykube app. Some packages include a fun 'scratch card' style reveal experience. Once revealed, you get full flight and hotel details immediately.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can I cancel or change my Flykube booking?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes, Flykube offers flexible cancellation and date change options. If your plans shift, their customer service team (available in Spanish, Portuguese, and English) can help you adjust your booking. Specific cancellation terms may vary by package type, so it is worth reviewing the details during checkout.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What airports does Flykube depart from?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Flykube operates from major airports across Spain and Portugal, including Madrid, Barcelona, Lisbon, Porto, Málaga, Valencia, and several others. The available departure airports are shown during the booking process so you can select the one closest to you.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
